The validator does not have access to your staked Tao and cannot take them, even if operating maliciously: your Tao is never forfeited nor are the additional gains you receive in the form of Tao at a rate of 82% of that validator’s rate.

Your original stake and rewards earned are never in jeopardy and can be unstaked at any time.
